					<description><![CDATA[Thank you GodFor the stars in the skyFor I do not know whyYou put them there for me to seeExcept for their beauty Thank you GodFor the memory of youthAnd for every toothThat I lostThat came backBetter and strongerAnd thank you GodFor every lossThat made&#160;<a class="read-more" href="https://llgt.cafe/thank-god">&#8230;</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Thank you God<br>For the stars in the sky<br>For I do not know why<br>You put them there for me to see<br>Except for their beauty</p>



<p>Thank you God<br>For the memory of youth<br>And for every tooth<br>That I lost<br>That came back<br>Better and stronger<br>And thank you God<br>For every loss<br>That made me<br>Stronger</p>



<p>Thank you God<br>For loving me<br>And for dying for me<br>Hung<br>On that tree<br>So that I might know you<br>My God</p>



<p>And thank you God<br>For all that is hope<br>And though<br>I might mope<br>There is hope in you<br>Not of this world<br>For you God<br>You are my God</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
