					<description><![CDATA[Some daysJust wearySome daysJust dreary Not on fireEvery dayNot excitedIn every way It may be sunny outBut not insideI may be frowningOr smiling inside I’m not sure whyI feel as I doI’m not quire sureWhy I doThe things I do But I know thisThat God&#160;<a class="read-more" href="https://llgt.cafe/some-days">&#8230;</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Some days<br>Just weary<br>Some days<br>Just dreary</p>



<p>Not on fire<br>Every day<br>Not excited<br>In every way</p>



<p>It may be sunny out<br>But not inside<br>I may be frowning<br>Or smiling inside</p>



<p>I’m not sure why<br>I feel as I do<br>I’m not quire sure<br>Why I do<br>The things I do</p>



<p>But I know this<br>That God is good<br>And he lives me me<br>And this is why<br>My life is good<br>Because<br>God lives in me</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
