										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Look around and<br>See<br>It may be you<br>It may be me</p>



<p>It may be your mother<br>Your sister<br>Your brother<br>Your father</p>



<p>If you see a need<br>A hug<br>Or to feed<br>Do what you will<br>Do what you can<br>To meet someone’s need<br>And be someone’s angel</p>



<p>&#8220;Therefore all things whatsoever ye would that men should do to you, do ye even so to them: for this is the law and the prophets.&#8221; &#8212; Matthew 7:12 (KJV)</p>
