					<description><![CDATA[Money, moneyYou’re so funnyYou hop awayLike a bunny You fly awayLike a birdThrough the skyWithout a word You come and goFrom things I earnTo things I oweA little joyA little woeWhere do you goI do not know You are a toolA teaching schoolYou teach the&#160;<a class="read-more" href="https://llgt.cafe/money">&#8230;</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Money, money<br>You’re so funny<br>You hop away<br>Like a bunny</p>



<p>You fly away<br>Like a bird<br>Through the sky<br>Without a word</p>



<p>You come and go<br>From things I earn<br>To things I owe<br>A little joy<br>A little woe<br>Where do you go<br>I do not know</p>



<p>You are a tool<br>A teaching school<br>You teach the wise<br>You teach the fool<br>To trust in God<br>No matter what<br>Whether little<br>Or plenty<br>It does not last<br>It hops away<br>Like a bunny<br>And flies away<br>Without a word<br>But goes somewhere else<br>To teach them, too</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
