		<title>I Give Permission</title>
		<link>https://llgt.cafe/i-give-permission</link>
					<comments>https://llgt.cafe/i-give-permission#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[llgt]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:27:39 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Poetry]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[God]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[LLGT]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://llgt.cafe/?p=1223</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[I give permission to tryI give permission to cryI give permission to ask whyI give permission to sigh I give permission to loveI give permission to hugI give permission to beI give permission to me I give permission to laughI give permission to smileI give&#160;<a class="read-more" href="https://llgt.cafe/i-give-permission">&#8230;</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>I give permission to try<br>I give permission to cry<br>I give permission to ask why<br>I give permission to sigh</p>



<p>I give permission to love<br>I give permission to hug<br>I give permission to be<br>I give permission to me</p>



<p>I give permission to laugh<br>I give permission to smile<br>I give permission to hike<br>And to go a whole mile</p>



<p>I give permission to you<br>I give permission to me<br>To be what God<br>Crated us to be</p>



<p>I give permission to save<br>I give permission to spend<br>I give permission to receive<br>And permission to send</p>



<p>I give permission to make<br>I give permission to take<br>I give permission to create<br>And permission to break</p>



<p>But be careful what you break<br>Whether asleep or awake<br>Whether it be your art<br>Or someone’s heart<br>Do it in love<br>For God up above<br>Sees you<br>He sees what you do<br>And he loves<br>Others too</p>



<p>I give permission to try<br>To cry<br>To sigh<br>To love<br>To hug<br>To laugh and to smile<br>I give permission<br>For you<br>To be<br>You</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
