<p>Large pot<br>Boiling water<br>Salt<br>You and your daughter<br>Learning to cook<br>A simple dish<br>A count and water<br>A simple wish<br>To keep it simple<br>To make a dish<br>Of Mac and Cheese<br>A simple wish</p>



<p>Add the pasta<br>Let it boil<br>Maybe now and maybe later<br>A little oil<br>Let it boil and<br>Let it cook<br>Drain<br>Plastic or foil</p>



<p>What cheese?<br>Maybe American<br>Perhaps queso<br>Or Parmesan</p>



<p>Butter<br>Cheese<br>Combine and make<br>Add the sauce<br>And oven bake<br>Time together<br>Add the love<br>Jesus came<br>And sent the dove<br>God is truth<br>God is love</p>
